org.wonderly.jini2
Class JiniAccess<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.wonderly.jini2.JiniAccess<T>

public class JiniAccess<T>
extends Object

This class provides support for simple lookup interfaces to the Jini LUS. It uses the ServiceDiscoveryManager which has some limitations related to callbacks. The SDM also requires sdm-dl.jar (or its contents) to be in the codebase.
